    "description": {
      "value": "<h4><span id=\"Darkflare\"><a name=\"TOC-Darkflare\"></a>Darkflare</span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> PCh:FG</p>\r\n<p>Created by the <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/monster-listings/humanoids/drow-common\">drow</a>-hunters, this alchemical flare explodes in black sparks 1 round after lighting. Any creature in the same square as a darkflare when it explodes must make a DC 15 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fortitude</a> save or be unable to see with <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a> for 1d10 rounds. Affected creatures can still see in normal light with no penalty. A darkflare has no effect on creatures without <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/special-abilities#TOC-Darkvision\">darkvision</a>. The DC to create a darkflare with <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) is 20.</p>\r\n",
